HEADWORD: Chloridate
<hw>Chlo"ri*date</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To treat or
prepare with a chloride, as a plate with chloride of silver, for the
purposes of photography.</def> <rj><au>R. Hunt.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

